---
title: Roasted Butternut Squash and Halloumi Jumble
description: Apparently, some chefs recommend soaking halloumi in buttermilk for two days before eating it. Our chefs thought they might try this, but owing to the fact that they’re pretty greedy (and really like halloumi), they’ve never been able to wait that long!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-butternut-squash-and-hal-b1f9b9d4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/roasted-butternut-squash-and-hal-f31ea8a6.pdf
